  "response": "Yes, there are several Monster Hunter games available on PC. The most notable ones include:\n\n1. **Monster Hunter: World** \u2013 Released for PC in August 2018, this game brought many new players to the series with its expansive world, improved graphics, and enhanced gameplay mechanics. \n\n2. **Monster Hunter Rise** \u2013 Released for PC in January 2022, this title built on the mechanics of Monster Hunter: World and included new gameplay features such as the Wirebug and the ability to ride certain monsters. \n\nBoth games have received significant updates and additional content after their initial release. Other titles from the Monster Hunter series may also be available on PC, but these are the primary entries in recent years.",
